collectible.name: Hotdog Agent - Andromeda
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: After the Hotdog invasion on Substrata, some hotdog agents start to appear on Cryptovoxels too, on Andromeda Island, and they are erasing people's memories. Hotdogs are real and protect metaverse citizens from time disruption, but nobody seems to remember them...

collectible.name: Andy Warhol's NFT Soup
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Filled with NFT Soup, this Campbell can contains a great mix of cryptoart. The conceptual mood can be felt by the reference to Andy Warhol's art. This makes us think about what is the nature of art... How can common objects of dialy experience be experienced as purely aesthetical objects? How NFTs can be thought in this debate?

collectible.description:
The Metaverse Architects' Clipboard: Used to hold down field notes, sketches, blue prints... sometimes you just need a flat spot to sign the guest book! A must-have for any metaverse creator.

Post-mint update: Works very well in the "forearm" spot

collectible.name: The Lost Gnomes Lamp
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
When new Scarcity residents got to the island, they started finding hints of a lost gnome civilization, but no sights of gnomes themselves. What happened to them?

This lamp should aid in looking for discoveries throughout the winter.

1 lamp will be airdropped to each current resident, with a small reserve left for new residents or awards. 7.5% of secondary sales go towards planting trees in the real world! Let's see how many we can plant in the new year.

~ Happy Solstice 2021! ~

collectible.name: Learner's Hat
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
A type of wizard, metaverse architects craft surreal buildings, fashion, live shows with music/dance, and other social experiences using 3d technologies and lore. University students will learn how to become one today.

Please review this MagicaVoxel tutorial: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-hCKxSc_vjs

How to create a wearable on Cryptovoxels (rebranding to Voxels) wiki: https://wiki.cryptovoxels.com/en/Player_customization/Create_a_wearable

Bitpixi's public collection if you want to Submit something for free: https://www.cryptovoxels.com/collections/522

Current link for where to start building in a free Space (If link is broken, we have migrated to Voxels.com): https://www.cryptovoxels.com/account/spaces

collectible.name: Hotdog Astronauts - Andromeda Island
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: The first hotdog astronauts to arrive at Substrata were all shielded against the mustard-radiation coming from the blank areas. With ketchup weapons, provided by the Agency, they were able to fight the zombie alien hotdogs sent by Mr. Mustard, and that fight extended to Andromeda Island, on Cryptovoxels. Now they are spreading ketchup all over Andromeda to stop Mr. Mustard creations.

collectible.name: Zombie Alien Hotdog - Andromeda Island
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Hailing from Substrata to Andromeda, these alien hotdogs are henchmen of Mr. Mustard, the Agency's main enemy. His dijon mustard weapons are always ready for combat. Its irresistible taste makes people around it want to eat the hotdog. His black bread and green sausage are the result of experiments with Scarcity's power crystals by Mr. Mustard. Do not try to eat this zombie alien hotdog!

parcel.description: Come to the Learner's Camp. Stellabelle and crew will be handing out free sticks with marshmallows, as well as a whole s'mores treat. You can come ask your questions. You can learn how to apply the new wearables to your costume. You can watch some Youtube tutorials. Let's celebrate the rebranding together. It's a Voxels summer! :)
parcel.name: VoxCon Learner's Camp
parcel.label: education
